      <h2>1. Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>We do <strong>not</strong> collect, store, share, or sell personal or sensitive information inside the app. If you send us a message via email or WhatsApp, we will receive the details you include in that message (e.g., name, preferred date, car model) solely to respond to your inquiry.</p>

      <h2>2. Permissions</h2>
      <p>The app does not request access to your location, contacts, camera, microphone, or storage.</p>

      <h2>3. Booking Form</h2>
      <p>When you submit the booking form, your message is prepared in your mail client and addressed to our team at
        <a href="mailto:rent@monquotidien.ink">rent@monquotidien.ink</a>
        (CC: <a href="mailto:support@monquotidien.ink">support@monquotidien.ink</a>).
        We do not store these details in the app; they reside in your and our email accounts.</p>

      <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>The app does not include analytics, ads, or trackers. When you choose to contact us via WhatsApp or email, your use of those services is governed by their respective privacy policies.</p>

      <h2>5. Images and Content</h2>
      <p>Car photos and descriptions are illustrative. They do not imply ownership or third-party endorsement.</p>

      <h2>6. Children’s Privacy</h2>
      <p>The app is not directed to children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect data from them.</p>

      <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
